{"tid":644403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(正義熱狗) 鄭錦滿:  民主黨議員應出聲炮轟許智峯","createTime":"2018-04-27T08:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T23:18:29.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"93432b2be6440ac98a4df391d1532697150e3e14","tid":644403,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:19:38.000Z","msg":"四眼講完呢段野後, 黃碧雲都加入炮轟許智峯了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/passiontimes/photos/a.1542479822481846.1073742090.420361564693683/1810006655729160/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpassiontimes%2Fphotos%2Fa.1542479822481846.1073742090.420361564693683%2F1810006655729160%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=ZYVhrGFvApibtd1c5U7j4TCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=78c44ea8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/passiontimes/photos/a.1542479822481846.1073742090.420361564693683/1810006655729160/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\nPassionTimes 熱血時報<br />\n讚好此專頁 &middot; 16小時 &middot; <br />\n <br />\n《熱血政治》<br />\n<br />\n第1168集：劉慧卿判許智峯死刑 女權撚黃碧雲沉默<br />\n<br />\n節目連結：<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/prog/83/1168\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fprog%2F83%2F1168&d=ZYVhrGFvApibtd1c5U7j4TCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=103c2d64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/prog/83/1168</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭錦滿：<br />\n<br />\n今日有傳閉路電視拍攝到民主黨立法會議員許智峯，不單止強搶女EO手機，而且糾纏期間仲有面貼面、環抱等大動作。<br />\n<br />\n無崗位的「民主黨元老」劉慧卿一如以往光速割蓆，表明許智峯不再適合當民主黨員以及立法會議員，中委會會議更一致通過即時凍結許智峯黨籍。另外男性企埋少少都大嗌性騷擾嘅黃碧雲，竟然冇為女受害人發聲。<br />\n<br />\n此事反映民主黨中不在其位的人仍舊眷戀鏡頭，喜歡指點江山；<strong>應該出聲的人卻刻意沉默，逃避責任，包藏禍心。</strong><br />\n<br />\n主持：鄭錦滿，Alvin，阿年<br />\n<br />\n嘉賓：Christine Wong<br />\n<br />\n首播日期：2018-4-26"},{"pid":"e8b1c80f5f5b478dbcf8266a4b9f312b35975d68","tid":644403,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:21:39.000Z","msg":"黃碧雲：許智峯的行為不能容忍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://linepost.hk/index.php/news/354-d20180426-7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flinepost.hk%2Findex.php%2Fnews%2F354-d20180426-7&d=ZYVhrGFvApibtd1c5U7j4TCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=ca4f8c5c\" target=\"_blank\">http://linepost.hk/index.php/news/354-d20180426-7</a>"},{"pid":"6ae6c1d2964ed83b9371a5107ab3fc472ec87a7a","tid":644403,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5b84c76a8bc9ef4acbc45e86bbf5bb16bffb46","tid":644403,"uid":1627,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:06:51.000Z","msg":"垃圾熱狗"},{"pid":"b898b8353d9db8dae61a57c7f6c4fb1394cabf02","tid":644403,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c5ed981a5dba5b668fced48c168f833a7f3704","tid":644403,"uid":30510,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:23:24.000Z","msg":"許智峯正正係幫完鄭松泰先搞到民主黨唔妥佢<br />\n熱狗都是義氣仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c7936477353d2182fefbad007391c2ab33f7ad","tid":644403,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T04:54:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a92ca24072217b7f4511ac42308d9ac0f2b66d6","tid":644403,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2c5ed981a5dba5b668fced48c168f833a7f3704","tid":644403,"uid":30510,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:23:24.000Z","msg":"許智峯正正係幫完鄭松泰先搞到民主黨唔妥佢<br />\n熱狗都是義氣仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T05:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c72b